OL,3,CCBI boss to warn Budget tax rises will
OL,4,C'hit growth' among UK businesses
OL,6,FTax rises in the autumn Budget are
OL,7,Fundermining investment among UK
OL,8,Fcompanies, according to the head of
OL,9,Fone of Britain's most prominent
OL,10,Fbusiness groups.
OL,12,FRain Newton-Smith, of the
OL,13,FConfederation of British Industry,
OL,14,Fwill say in a speech on Monday:
OL,15,F"Across the board, in so many sectors,
OL,16,Fmargins are being squeezed and profits
OL,17,Fare being hit by a tough trading
OL,18,Fenvironment that just got tougher.
