OL,3,CCBI boss to warn Budget tax rises will
OL,4,C'hit growth' among UK businesses
OL,6,F"And here's the rub, profits aren't
OL,7,Fjust extra money for companies to
OL,8,Fstuff in a pillowcase. Profits are
OL,9,Finvestment."
OL,11,FMs Newton-Smith will add: "When you
OL,12,Fhit profits, you hit competitiveness,
OL,13,Fyou hit investment, you hit growth."
OL,15,FLabour made economic growth a central
OL,16,Fpart of its pitch to voters in the
OL,17,Fgeneral election, and has repeatedly
OL,18,Fpledged to help boost business
OL,19,Finvestment since entering government.
