OL,3,CCBI boss to warn Budget tax rises will
OL,4,C'hit growth' among UK businesses
OL,6,FIn the October Budget, Chancellor
OL,7,FRachel Reeves announced a nearly #70
OL,8,Fbillion uplift in public spending,
OL,9,Fpartly funded by sharp increases in
OL,10,Fbusiness taxes like employer national
OL,11,Finsurance contributions.
OL,13,FLabour also raised the minimum wage,
OL,14,Fin a move praised by workers' groups
OL,15,Fand unions, but which businesses have
OL,16,Fsaid will force them to pass on some
OL,17,Fcosts to consumers, hire fewer people
OL,18,For make less profit.
