OL,4,C'hit growth' among UK businesses
OL,6,FIn a speech at the CBI's annual
OL,7,Fconference in London, Ms Newton-Smith
OL,8,Fwill point to a recent survey by the
OL,9,Fbody which found almost two-thirds of
OL,10,Fcompanies think the Budget will damage
OL,11,FUK investment.
