OL,6,FThe event is also due to be attended
OL,7,Fby the Chancellor, who is expected to
OL,8,Ftake part in an onstage talk with
OL,9,FScottish Power chief executive Keith
OL,10,FAnderson.
OL,12,FMs Newton-Smith will say: "Tax rises
OL,13,Flike this must never again be simply
OL,14,Fdone to business.
OL,16,F"That's the road to unintended
OL,17,Fconsequences. From now on we need an
OL,18,Felevated partnership for a higher
OL,19,Fpurpose.
