OL,6,F"Too many businesses are having to
OL,7,Fcompromise on their plans for growth.
OL,8,FWe can't let that stand and not act."
OL,10,FMs Newton-Smith will also urge the
OL,11,Fgovernment to move faster on promises
OL,12,Fto reform business rates, give
OL,13,Fcompanies more flexibility on how they
OL,14,Fspend money via the apprenticeship
OL,15,Flevy, and make occupational health tax-
OL,16,Ffree to help fewer people drop out of
OL,17,Fthe workforce.
